AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025 - Apply Online for 08 Assistant Professor Posts
Prasanna / All Government Jobs / Aug 18, 2025, 15:06 IST
 All India Institute of Medical Science
 8 Jobs |  Posted On : 18-Aug-2025 |  Jammu and Kashmir |  Salary : 152,250 to 152,250




FOLLOW

The All India Institute of Medical Sciences Jammu (AIIMS Jammu) has declared the latest job notification for 2025. To fill up the vacancies for 08 Assistant Professor Jobs. Those candidates who have qualified in the MBBS, MS/ MD, M.Ch. can grab this chance and apply for the AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025. Here we include the age limit, selection process, salary structure, education details, application fee, and how to apply for these posts. Interested and eligible candidates can apply online through the website on or before the last date of application. For more details, visit the official website.




If you are looking for more, here is a list of Government Jobs in 2025 that you can all apply for. Use this link for more jobs in Jammu and Kashmir.

AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025 - Eligibility Criteria
Name of the Posts	No.of Vacancies	Qualification
Assistant Professor 	08	MBBS, MS/ MD, M.Ch

Age Limit for the AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Age Limit: 21 years.
The Maximum Age Limit: 50 years.

Selection Process for the AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025

Written Test
Interview

Salary Structure for the AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025

The Minimum Salary: Rs. 1,52,250 /- per month.

Application fee for the AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025

For all candidates Rs: 1,000 /-
How to Apply for the AIIMS Jammu Recruitment 2025
Visit the official website.
Go to the recruitment or career page.
Check for the Assistant Professor Jobs 2025.
Read the notification carefully.
Check the eligibility criteria.
If you meet the eligibility criteria.
Click on the Apply Online link.
Register with yur mobile number and password.
Fill out the mandatory details carefully.
Pay the application fee.
Submit the application form and take a printout of the application form for further reference.

Important Dates

Starting Date of Application	16-08-2025
Last Date of Application	25-08-2025
